  "translations": {
    "en": "\"The companions of the right hand - how blessed are the companions of the right hand! The companions of the left hand - how wretched are the companions of the left hand! And the foremost are the foremost\" (56:8-10),",
    "ur": "\"اصحاب میمنہ، کیا ہیں اصحاب میمنہ! اصحاب مشئمہ! اور سبقت لے جانے والے\" (56:8-10)،",
    "tr": "\"Sağ ehli, ne mutlu! Sol ehli! Ve öne geçenler, öne geçenler\" (56:8-10),",
    "fa": "«اصحاب میمنه چه اصحاب میمنه‌ای! اصحاب مشئمه! و پیشتازان» (56:8-10)،",
    "id": "\"Golongan kanan, alangkah mulianya! Golongan kiri! Dan orang terdahulu\" (56:8-10),",
    "bn": "\"ডানদিকের সঙ্গীরা, কত ধন্য! বামদিকের সঙ্গীরা! আর অগ্রবর্তীরা\" (৫৬:৮-১০),",
    "es": "\"Los compañeros de la derecha, ¡bienaventurados! Los de la izquierda! Y los primeros\" (56:8-10),",
    "fr": "\"Les compagnons de la droite ! Les compagnons de la gauche ! Et les premiers\" (56:8-10),",
    "de": "\"Die Gefährten der Rechten! Die Gefährten der Linken! Und die Vorauseilenden\" (56:8-10),",
    "ru": "«Обладатели правой стороны! Обладатели левой! И опередившие» (56:8-10),",
    "zh": "\"右边的人们何等幸福！左边的人们！先行者们\"（56:8-10），"
  }
